; Swimnerd 6-Digit Racing Clock - FinishLynx LSS Script
; Copyright (c) 2026 Swimnerd
;
; Serial Settings (adjust as needed): 9600,8,N,1
; TCP Settings (if networked): -1,0.0.0.0,1024
;
; This script sends timing data to a 6-digit racing clock
; Format: MM:SS.HH (minutes, seconds, hundredths)
;
; 6-digit display shows: [M][M]:[S][S].[H][H]
; Example: 01:23.45

;;Initialization
; Sent once when FinishLynx starts
; Clear display or send initialization command
\10\00INIT\0d\0a

;;TimeRunning
; Sent while race clock is running
; Send formatted time (MM:SS.HH)
\11\01%s\0d\0a

;;TimeStopped
; Sent when race clock stops
; Send final time
\11\01%s\0d\0a

;;TimeUpdate
; Sent periodically (every second) while running
\11\01%s\0d\0a

;;Result
; Sent when results are finalized
; Show winning time on clock
\14\06%s\0d\0a
